modName: Bijin NPCs - The Ordinary Women Patch
summary: Merged Bijin NPC .esp for Adrianne, Karliah, Rikke, Sapphire and Vex
descriptionHtml:
Merged Bijin NPC .esp for Adrianne, Karliah, Rikke, Sapphire and Vex, others are managed by The Ordinary Women.
If you use both Bijin NPCs and The Ordinary Women you will encounter black/dark face bug, this patch fixes it.
Bijin NPCs - https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/71054/
The Ordinary Women - https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70547/
USLEEP Patch - https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/79112/?
author: rxkx22
